## 3. Random Password Generator 

## Objective
A secure password generator application that creates strong, random passwords with customizable options. The application includes password strength evaluation and clipboard integration for easy copying.

## Features
- Customizable password length (4-32 characters)
- Character type selection (Letters, Numbers, Symbols)
- Password strength analysis
- Auto-copy to clipboard
- Exclude similar characters option (i, l, 1, O, 0)
- Visual strength indicator (Weak/Moderate/Strong)
- One-click copy functionality
- Modern, intuitive GUI

## Technologies Used
- **Python 3.x**
- **Tkinter** - GUI framework
- **Random** - Password generation
- **String** - Character sets
- **Pyperclip** - Clipboard operations

## Project Structure
Password Generator/
└── randompass.py 
